{
  "stem": "5758.2",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My brother Eric did go.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in the meantime, the November the 9th came, the Kristallnacht.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] This was a terrible, terrible night that I remember.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know whether you know the story why, actually.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a-- a-- a Polish Jew who killed a German diplomat in Paris.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the German took this as an excuse and burned all the [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] synagogues.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In fact, I must tell you, I don't know whether you had-- I read the details of how the-- there was a historian who wrote in Vienna how many synagogues were burnt and how many people.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Can I-- I have some notes here, [INAUDIBLE]?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If you'd like to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, it's just--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--if it's historic, it will be documented.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It is-- yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, because there in Vienna, there were 21 synagogues burnt-- synagogues burned down, 4,053 Jewish shops plundered and closed, 1,950 Jewish homes were ransacked, 7,800 Jews arrested. 680 Jews committed suicide, and 91 Jews were murdered.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a night, again, when I-- which I will not forget.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because as I told you before, we lived on the third floor of an apartment building.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Our windows were overlooking a courtyard, and we saw the flames.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The-- there-- this-- the-- the-- the sky was red from flames.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got a telephone call from a-- a very good friend of ours, [NON-ENGLISH] were the name, who lived on the other side of the courtyard overlooking [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was our synagogue there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he phoned us up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, do you know-- to my parents-- do you know that our synagogue is burning completely?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's completely burning.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
